{"type":"message","id":"1eb622b2","parentId":"dc1d05f8","timestamp":"2026-02-27T09:48:28.886Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\n从日志中我找到了关键问题！\n\n**错误信息**：`telegram message failed: Network request for 'sendMessage' failed!`\n\n这说明 **Gateway 服务虽然重启了，但仍然没有正确使用代理环境变量**。\n\n**问题分析**：\n1. ✅ 我们创建了 `/Users/hope/.openclaw/gateway.env` 文件\n2. ✅ Gateway 服务已重启  \n3. ❌ **LaunchAgent 没有加载我们的环境变量文件**\n\n**根本原因**：\nmacOS 的 LaunchAgent 服务不会自动读取 `.env` 文件，需要在 plist 配置文件中显式设置环境变量。\n\n**解决方案**：\n\n让我检查并修改 LaunchAgent 配置文件：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_472999cdc35d4b65bb0d7eab","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/Library/LaunchAgents/ai.openclaw.gateway.plist"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":128107,"output":193,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128300,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772185659744}}
