{"type":"message","id":"d1658372","parentId":"fe34942e","timestamp":"2026-02-27T12:44:50.590Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## 📊 Main Agent\n\n哈哈，看来终于成功了！🎉 \n\n是的，经过一系列的配置调整（代理环境变量、LaunchAgent 配置、模型代理设置等），现在 **OpenClaw 的 Telegram 集成终于正常工作了**！\n\n你现在可以：\n- ✅ 正常接收 OpenClaw 的消息\n- ✅ 通过 Telegram 与 OpenClaw 交互\n- ✅ 使用所有 Telegram 相关功能（发送消息、表情、贴纸等）\n\n如果还有其他问题或需要进一步配置，随时告诉我！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":140914,"output":119,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141033,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772196236709}}
